        "subject": "LU-6142 obd: remove macro layer for struct md_ops",
        "message": "LU-6142 obd: remove macro layer for struct md_ops\n\nPorting patches to the upstream client related\nto the struct md_ops proved to overly complex\ndue to the various macros employed. Since macros\nare frowned on upstream lets remove the needless\nmacro abstraction layer.\n\nChange-Id: I52b35a9de482e56d93b322e7e2b103d4a5577dbc\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@yahoo.com>\n"
